in terms of the kind

00:09:54.410 --> 00:09:56.620
of clever titles [laughter].

00:09:56.620 --> 00:10:01.630
One of the, did it get to a
point that was made earlier

00:10:01.630 --> 00:10:07.280
about the writing well for winds,
I haven't been able to spend time

00:10:07.280 --> 00:10:09.480
with the score, but I believe
that there's certain focuses

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:11.990
on different instruments
in the kind of the interim,

00:10:11.990 --> 00:10:14.370
