Just knowing that these are going
to be, that there's a chops issue

00:10:30.890 --> 00:10:33.140
as well as other types of --

00:10:33.140 --> 00:10:35.140
&gt;&gt; Paul Lansky: Yeah, I
thought it would be a good way

00:10:35.140 --> 00:10:38.000
to exercise the different
things that instruments can do.

00:10:38.000 --> 00:10:39.810
I saved the last one
