that's very important

00:20:22.470 --> 00:20:27.780 position:56%
to us throughout our careers because
we find that audiences will relate

00:20:27.780 --> 00:20:30.560
to a piece of new music that
they haven't heard before

00:20:30.560 --> 00:20:33.130
if they can relate to
the story behind it.

00:20:33.130 --> 00:20:35.730
If they can understand
where it's coming from,

00:20:35.730 --> 00:20:38.000
even before they've heard it, then
that's something that they're going

00:20:38.000 --> 00:20:41.030
to be able to appreciate without
ever having heard it before.

00:20:41.030 --> 00:20:46.460
